student yet.

00:03:27.666 --> 00:03:29.870
There's no way I could
support you.

00:03:29.970 --> 00:03:31.005
If you needed something,

00:03:31.105 --> 00:03:33.176
even if it was a matter of
life and death,

00:03:33.276 --> 00:03:34.580
there wouldn't be much I
could do.

00:03:34.680 --> 00:03:38.186
That sort of thing is
hard for a man to deal with.

00:03:38.286 --> 00:03:40.123
You've gotta understand.

00:03:42.428 --> 00:03:44.733
- Okay, then I'll go home,
find some work,

00:03:44.833 --> 00:03:47.471
and save up enough money to
move to Tokyo.

00:03:47.572 --> 00:03:50.945
Once you've passed the
university entrance exams next
year

00:03:51.045 --> 00:03:51.847
I'll come and join.

00:03:51.947 --> 00:03:53.951
You I'll even get myself a job

00:03:54.051 --> 00:03:55.354
so you won't have to support me.

00:03:55.454 --> 00:03:57.191
I'll make it on my own.

00:03:58.126 --> 00:04:00.297
So what do you think of that?

00:04:01.700 --> 00:04:04.438
- I guess I'm gonna have to
pass those entrance exams.

