- Ah, forget it.

00:04:55.942 --> 00:04:58.480
(Shoji groans)

00:04:58.581 --> 00:04:59.516
- Okay, fine. I'll say it.

00:04:59.616 --> 00:05:02.287
A man's gotta do what
a man's gotta do.

