I'm not gonna sleep

00:05:07.565 --> 00:05:10.237
with some made up foreign
guy named Michael.

00:05:10.337 --> 00:05:12.408
I don't wanna sleep
with anyone, but you.

00:05:12.509 --> 00:05:13.544
- Huh?

00:05:16.115 --> 00:05:18.219
I'll make some tea, okay?

00:05:19.556 --> 00:05:23.831
Can I offer you some black
tea or green tea, Michael?

