00:08:17.177 --> 00:08:19.481
I'll show you, demon lord.

00:08:30.370 --> 00:08:34.378
- I don't know where I was
born. I've never met my father.

00:08:34.478 --> 00:08:35.748
And I haven't seen my mother for
so long

