I moved to the city by
the sea when I was four.

00:08:42.896 --> 00:08:44.966
I was raised by my grandmother
who ran a restaurant

00:08:45.066 --> 00:08:48.674
and who constantly dumped
her cold sarcasm on me.

00:08:48.774 --> 00:08:53.283
Now I'm working my ass off,
polishing the shards of a dream.

