00:11:07.618 --> 00:11:09.823
when women were screaming for
me.

00:11:09.923 --> 00:11:12.528
- But they all dressed as Nana,
doesn't that freak you out?

00:11:12.628 --> 00:11:16.035
- [Nana Osaki] Wow,
it's a jacket. So cool.

